| 101 | soap       |   122 |
| 102 | maggie     |    26 |
| 103 | jelly      |     3 |
| 104 | dinner set |  1020 |
| 105 | book       |   510 |
| 106 | tea        |   255 |
| 107 | dairymilk  |    61 |
